    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 1994 Nissan 300ZX Twin Turbo featuring the iconic VG30DETT power plant. This Z32 maintains factory-spec Garrett T25 turbochargers with consistent boost pressure and no shaft play. The drivetrain features a precision 5-speed manual transmission mated to a viscous limited-slip differential (VLSD). Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive 120k-mile service: timing belt, tensioners, water pump, and new cam seals. The Super HICAS rear-steering system remains fully functional, and the suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings to eliminate deflection. Cooling is managed by an upgraded dual-core aluminum radiator. This is a driver-spec machine with excellent compression and a sorted vacuum system, ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Reliable daily driver. Clean title. Well-maintained interior. Minor exterior wear. Mechanically sound.",
