    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior finish remains vibrant and smooth, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Step inside to find a cabin that has been kept in impressive condition; the seating surfaces are firm and clean, and all electronic systems\u2014from the infotainment to the climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the car reflects a history of diligent ownership, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from regular, documented oil changes and inspections. With healthy tire tread and a recent professional detail, this car offers a refined driving experience and the peace of mind that comes from a vehicle that has been truly cared for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
